{"tid":1498134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極反智！關於9月2中學生罷課！","createTime":"2019-08-23T09:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T19:18:15.000Z","uid":303943,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"110ca517870c2a11a366209049f286127a62c580","tid":1498134,"uid":303943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"遊行<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">唔出不反對通知書</span></span> 你地又肯<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">照出照行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁點解罷課就一定要聽足學校枝笛？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n出面遊行 出反對通知書<br />\n明知會犯法告暴動坐10年<br />\n都照出<br />\n<br />\n咁點解學校一句唔比 一句反對 點解就真係聽？<br />\n你驚比人記名？<br />\n咁之後呢？<br />\n諗下後果會係啲咩先<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">最多扣分 記小過 記大過 見家長 </span><br />\n點會咁易停你學 根本唔洗驚<br />\n你係做緊啲岩嘅事<br />\n<br />\n出面班手足<span style=\"color: orange;\">食子彈 被捕 班狗濫權 亂打人 催淚彈後遺症 </span>等等 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">無得投訴 唔知no 無得見律師 無得去廁所 無人權</span><br />\n<br />\n佔個hall風險其實好細<br />\n加上好多老師支持呢次運動<br />\n佢地都係口硬心軟 自己人多<br />\n<br />\n中學生嘅你地 自己判斷啦 <br />\n我想帶出係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無野係必須服從架 </span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"49a27d6cb3aa51b174b3cbb2aea4479fbc0d6b6d","tid":1498134,"uid":303943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"6e95841a9a82e466038f571e14ae1036d61082c8","tid":1498134,"uid":303943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"再推多下"},{"pid":"142d699ed867edbdd6cce28e399894d7dfdd6586","tid":1498134,"uid":303943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T09:28:27.000Z","msg":"推多下"},{"pid":"ade9f366e22532688b6f50d6333ba29cb6159511","tid":1498134,"uid":303943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"